## 📡 API Documentation

### 🔐 Authentication APIs

#### Register User
```http
POST /api/auth/register
```

Request Body:
```json
{
  "name": "Anvitha",
  "email": "anvitha@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}
```

#### Login User
```http
POST /api/auth/login
```

Request Body:
```json
{
  "email": "anvitha@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}
```

Response:
```json
{
  "token": "jwt_token",
  "role": "admin"
}
```

