### 📋 Lead APIs

> All lead routes require JWT token in Authorization header.

Example:
```http
Authorization: Bearer your_token
```

#### Get All Leads
```http
GET /api/leads
```

Query Parameters:
- `search`
- `status`
- `source`
- `sort`
- `page`

#### Create Lead
```http
POST /api/leads
```

Request Body:
```json
{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@gmail.com",
  "status": "Qualified",
  "source": "Website"
}
```

#### Update Lead
```http
PUT /api/leads/:id
```

#### Delete Lead
```http
DELETE /api/leads/:id
```